channel.title: Weird Problem!
channel.description: I'm having a problem with the server I always use. The IP is highscape.tar.cc and it's supposed to be up for 15 minutes and go down for 2 minutes. Anyway, when I try to log on, it logs me right back out. Is it possible I could be banned? The owner never told me I was banned and I don't remember doing anything wrong. Someone please help!
